{"type": "article", "id": 5733, "title": "Herschel Supply Co. 2015 春季 Studio 系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-30T07:48:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233916b9dp7Xo2M1VveR3s.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t我们前两天刚刚推荐了加拿大人气包袋品牌 Herschel Supply Co. 今年春夏以中世纪建筑与沙漠风格为主题的包袋系列，而昨日该品牌又带来了全新的春季 Studio 系列，包括一款 Settlement 背包、一款 Chapter 杂物包、Alexander 托特包、Sutton Mid 旅行袋以及特别款 Folio XL 手拿包，全部以黑白两色的主色调进行呈现，简约中透出大气与酷劲。设计团队选用了防水性能极佳的柏油帆布制作包身，提手处采用了安全带专用的尼龙材质，赋予了这一系列包袋极强的实用性。定价 39.99－129.99 美元（约合人民币 250－812 元）不等，<a href=\"http://shop.herschelsupply.ca/collections/studio\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052339143o46m8B5NAcJQGZg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233914qbruvgTHow8sVCUN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233915Iy4bmq1hBuHxp92S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052339157jXC0uivWYEl4HBh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233915I7w1HLCARG8xXPd6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233916viXWGBuotN7ndfPk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}